recipe.name: Sweet Potato Cake
recipe.preparation: Melt 1 cube margerine in pan.  Cool.  Stir in 1 egg + 1 jar jr size baby food sweet potatoes.  Stir.  Add 1 small can crushed pineapple, drained.Sift 1 1/4 cup flour with 1 cup sugar, 1 tsp soda, 2 tsp cinnamon + 1/2 tsp salt.  Add to above + stir with fork  Add 1 cup chopped nuts + bake 325F for 45 minsFrosting:1 small pkg cream cheese2 Tbsp butter1/2 pkg powdered sugar1 tsp vanilla
